		<section>
			<title>Plugin Prerequisites</title>
			<para>
				The plugin has the following prerequisites;
				<itemizedlist>
					<listitem>
						<para>a Java 5 or higher JDK,</para>
						<para>
							To download the latest release of the Sun JDK, go to
							<ulink url="http://developers.sun.com/downloads/"/>, and download the latest Java 6 JDK or
							an older Java 5 JDK, either will work but Java 6 is recommended.
						</para>
					</listitem>
					<listitem>
						<para>a <trademark class="registered">Atlassian JIRA</trademark> 4.0 or higher installation,</para>
						<para>
							Please refer to <ulink url="http://www.atlassian.com/software/jira"/> for details on
							obtaining a copy of Atlassian Jira for your project/community or business.
						</para>
					</listitem>
					<listitem>
						<para>a Hudson installation.</para>
						<para>
						</para>
					</listitem>
				</itemizedlist>
			</para>
